<div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent"><br />is there any commerce game that do toggle the A12 line to trigger an irq?<br /></div><br /><br />The way to test this in an emulator is to "mark" the IRQ counter whenever the A12 line is toggled from 0 to 1 via PPU register writes, then log an occurrence if this marked counter value causes an IRQ. Anything which resets the counter would "unmark" it.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=17">blargg</a> — Sat May 20, 2006 12:22 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
